title: Ghost of Dragstrip Hollow

overview: Matter-transmitter sabotage leaves a British scientist (Bryant Halliday) disfigured and full of amps.
tagline: Horror of Horrors!
title: The Projected Man

overview: A Semester at Sea ship is attacked and sunk by a mutated two-headed shark, and the survivors seek refuge on a deserted atoll. The coeds, however, are no longer safe when the atoll starts flooding.
tagline: 1 Body, 2 Heads and 6,000 Teeth
title: 2-Headed Shark Attack

overview: Eric Binford watches a lot of movies. He is the truest definition of a film geek. One day, his sanity takes a turn for the worse and he begins acting out his favorite scenes from the movies. In doing so, he manages to involve his enemies and the scenes usually result in death.
tagline: Meet Eric Binford, the ultimate movie buff. If you know someone like him… run!
title: Fade to Black

overview: Janey arrives at a silent retreat in the middle of the woods for rehabilitation, only to discover that the men who run it aren't afraid to show her what lurks beyond the trees.
tagline: The only way to escape the silence is to scream
title: Silent Retreat

overview: A black hole hits North Wisconsin and opens a door to other dimensions. Giant 15 meter spiders emerge from it, who have an appetite for human flesh! Dr. Jenny Langer and Dr. Vance from the NASA try to save the world.
tagline: Creeping!...Crawling!...Crushing!
title: The Giant Spider Invasion

overview: A woman escapes a group of bullies seeking to rape her and takes refuge with a seemingly kind couple who have a dark secret hidden in their quiet, secluded house.
title: The Last House in the Woods

overview: Citizens of a small town are infected by a biological weapon that causes its victims to become violently insane. As uninfected citizens struggle to survive, the military readies its own response.
tagline: All hell is about to break loose.
title: The Crazies

overview: Group of heroin smugglers finds shelter on abandoned oil rig after their ship had exploded. Soon they find that the oil rig was just cover for biological experiment. One of the results is Charlie - shape-shifting monster with ability to absorb the memory of its victims. However, even such creatures have their own bad habits.
tagline: In the middle of the ocean, a new form of horror is taking shape.
title: Proteus
